{"title": "It Is Never Too Late to Mend", "description": "A ruthless squire becomes obsessed with a younger woman and conspires against her lover, George Fielding, so that the squire can win her. With the squire's financial pressure turned up on his family, George goes to Australia to earn money enough to marry his girl. In the meantime, a young man named Tom Robinson is sent to prison for stealing. For his somewhat minor offense, he suffers severe mistreatment in prison. \"It Is Never Too Late to Mend\" was written in the 1850s to shed light on abuses in British prison discipline and the treatment of criminals, but is also an adventure yarn set in the gold fields of Australia. (Summary by TriciaG)", "duration": 96451, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "8464", "name": "Charles Reade"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/nevertoolatetomend_1903_librivox/mend_1903.jpg", "copyright_year": "1856", "genres": ["Action & Adventure Fiction", "Culture & Heritage Fiction", "Published 1800 -1900"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "TriciaG"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "TriciaG"}], "sections": [{"section": 1, "title": "Chapter I, part 1", "readers": [11884], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/nevertoolatetomend_1903_librivox/itisnevertoolatetomend_01_reade_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1541}, {"section": 2, "title": "Chapter I, part 2", "readers": [11884], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/nevertoolatetomend_1903_librivox/itisnevertoolatetomend_02_reade_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1818}, {"section": 3, "title": "Chapter II", "readers": [12059], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/nevertoolatetomend_1903_librivox/itisnevertoolatetomend_03_reade_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1893}, {"section": 4, "title": "Chapter III", "readers": [6311], "path": "http://www.archive.org/download/nevertoolatetomend_1903_librivox/itisnevertoolatetomend_04_r